
## Architecture Pipeline

```bash
+-------------------+        +--------------------------+
| User in Browser   | -----> | Popup UI (v2-extension)  |
| Adds keywords     |        | add/remove/scan controls |
+-------------------+        +------------+-------------+
                                          |
                                          | chrome.runtime message
                                          v
                               +----------+-----------+
                               | Background Worker    |
                               | routing + decisions  |
                               +----+-------------+---+
                                    |             |
                     local scan path|             |web scrap path
                                    |             |
                                    v             v
                      +-------------+--+   +------+------------------+
                      | Content Script |   | Web Scrap Service       |
                      | read img attrs |   | localhost:8787          |
                      | apply blur CSS |   | express + cheerio + api |
                      +--------+-------+   +-----------+-------------+
                               ^                       |
                               | matched image URLs    |
                               +-----------------------+
```

